title: THE GEORGE BURNS SHOW -- with Jack Benny, Betty Grable, etc...
description:
A year after the cancellation of his own sitcom, and while Gracie Allen was enjoying her retirement, George Burns worked on this NBC special from mid 1960. 
It featured Jack Benny, Betty Grable, Bobby Darin, 
and from the game show "To Tell the Truth" singer / actress Polly Bergen.

This show is in its original videotaped form, but the picture is a bit "fuzzy".
Not sure why -- it probably just needs some remastering.
Or it may just be a second-generation dub. Still looks sharp though!
